entries.femaleVariant: Wha--? Who-- Who the hell're you?!
What you'd find more interesting is who sent me.
I-I do, I remember well. It was an integral stage in my research. Y-you see we're working on new antibiotic--
This antibiotic of yours – I know for damn sure most of humanity couldn't afford it. I know its main purpose is to fatten your holiday bonus.
Scream your throat bloody. Not a soul's gonna hear you.
Remember your little science experiement with the Red Ocher Clan? The families send their regards.
I'm not! I know people like you. Hired plenty myself. And I know you won't let me go.
Oh, please. Gonna feed me the story of how sacrifices must be made in the quest to save humanity?
B-but at least let me back up the test results for future application. These nomads – they're gone regardless. Let their death serve a purpose!
Fine, do it... But don't pull any stunts, got it?
Oh, you sure about that? I think somethin' horrible happened to 'em. And it'll happen to you.
entries.maleVariant: You sure about that? 'Cause I think somethin' horrible happened to 'em. And it'll happen to you.

entries.femaleVariant: Fuck your data. You die here and now.
